 → CheckoutService延迟\n\n3. **与Log证据的强关联**：\n   - 故障时间窗口（2025-06-11T11:10:46Z至11:23:46Z）与Log中显示的Byteman agent注入时间完全一致\n   - AdService的严重延迟（10倍）与Log中显示的\"AdService--stress-1749640247 execute()\"高频执行（155次）直接对应\n   - 所有3个adservice实例同时异常，与Log中显示的3个节点故障模式一致\n\n4. **Metric数据的补充支持**：\n   - adservice的CPU使用率从0.01上升到0.6（60倍增长）与压力注入导致的资源消耗一致\n   - TiDB-PD内存使用异常可能由AdService异常查询引起，而非根因\n\n**结论**：调用链数据为Log专家的分析提供了强有力的支持，显示AdService的严重延迟是系统级问题的直接表现，而Chaos Mesh压力注入正是导致这一延迟的根本原因。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nDISAGREED", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "adservice is the root cause due to Chaos Mesh Byteman stress injection (AdService--stress-1749640247) causing pod_cpu_usage spike and severe rrt_max degradation", "current_task_instruction": "当前处于【分析阶段】。\n以下是你可以访问的全量上下文信息，包含了用户输入、当前假设、以及其他所有智能体的历史发现：\n================================\nUUID: 13ebf32d-216\n\nUser Query: A fault occurred from 2025-06-11T11:10:46Z to 2025-06-11T11:23:46Z. Please identify the root cause.\n\n\n[RAW DATA CONTEXT]\n\n--- Raw Log Data ---\n{'status': 'success', 'message': '成功加载日志数据。UUID: 13ebf32d-216，共 108 条错误日志', 'filtered_logs': 'node_name,service_name,pod_name,message,occurrence_count\\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,\"Exception in thread \"\"Attach Listener\"\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-03,adservice,adservice-0,Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,\"Exception in thread \"\"Attach Listener\"\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,Agent failed to start!,出现次数:2\\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,calling installed(AdService--stress-174